le=\"color: gold;\">612！721！811！你記得嗎？請香港人繼續走下去！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://im5.ezgif.com/tmp/ezgif-5-d5ebcebba7cd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fim5.ezgif.com%2Ftmp%2Fezgif-5-d5ebcebba7cd.gif&h=5f074275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">27/8(二) 動物界集會/遊行 轉場8.31民陣大遊行</span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhAWbhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhAWbhG.jpg&h=63a1860b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2wsp4CY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2wsp4CY.jpg&h=b919ba87&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">28/8(三) 圍堵國泰城 聲援航空界</span></span> <br />\n【圍堵國泰最新消息】職工盟申請的週三國泰城集會，遭到警方發出反對通知書，現已申請上訴，已要求遊行上訴委員會盡快展開聆訊，有進一步消息將立即向大家公布。<br />\n留意活動詳情請去 主辦單位 - 職公盟 Facebook  : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCTU%2F&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=61d73201\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCTU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0gWqO19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0gWqO19.png&h=4b43da2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">28/8 (三) 晚上八時 反送中 #metoo 集會</span></span><br />\n留意活動詳情請去 Telegram Group : <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ProtestTooHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FProtestTooHK&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=108e0bde\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ProtestTooHK</a><br />\n【置頂】828 metoo集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1505524/page/1/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1505524/page/1/</a><br />\nDress code (#Metoo 集會 ) 我地要做真正港女，保護香港！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1503841/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1503841/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/rjDMtHc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrjDMtHc.jpg&h=24322fd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndvfjoN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndvfjoN.jpg&h=d6acacc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">29/8 (四) 港九新界遍地開花放映會最新時間表</span></span><br />\n留意活動詳情請去  : <br />\n《凜冬烈火：烏克蘭為自由而戰》遍地開花放映會<br />\n<a href=\"http://timable.com/en/event/1843017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimable.com%2Fen%2Fevent%2F1843017&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=a19be1c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://timable.com/en/event/1843017</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/QNLbC63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNLbC63.jpg&h=12f02c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWinter on fire《凜冬烈火：烏克蘭自由之戰》<br />\n是一部2015年的紀錄片，由葉夫根尼&middot;艾菲尼夫斯基執導，紀錄了烏克蘭在2013年至2014年冬季爆發的親歐盟示威運動，這部紀錄片由烏克蘭、美國和英國聯合製作。本片於2015年10月9日在Netflix上釋出，在此之前曾數次參加電影節的展映。<br />\n<br />\nWinter on fire Trailer :<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RibAQHeDia8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRibAQHeDia8&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=83504dc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RibAQHeDia8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">31/8 (六) 下午三點 民陣「人大831落閘五周年」遊行  </span></span> <br />\n留意活動詳情請去 主辦單位 - 民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front Facebook  : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHu